data.description: Built 2020, this like-new home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and open concept floor plan. First floor features great room, office, formal dining area and large kitchen with island, stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Top floor bedrooms including large primary plus loft area. Screened-in Sun Patio with oversized stamped concrete pad, great outdoor living space ideal for entertaining! Move-In Ready!
